Maintainer: Duc Tran <duct@nevada.unr.edu>
Description: Single-cell Decomposition using Hierarchical Autoencoder (scDHA) is a fast and accurate pipeline for single-cell analyses. 
    The scDHA software package can perform clustering, dimension reduction and visualization, classification, and time-trajectory inference on single-cell data.
